					<div class="commentheading">On December 26, 2010 at 12:42 AM, chanman (guest) said...</div>
					<div class="commentsubject"></div>
					<div class="commentbody">@Jun<br />
<br />
Melting it in a double boiler will cause some separation.<br />
<br />
I've re-melted my ganache a few times and have a lump of fat-studded chocolate that I've scraped off the top of my bowl. Still trying to figure out what to do with it. Anyone have any ideas on how to cause the fat to re-emulsify?</div>
